Package org.omg.dds.pub

Interface PublisherListener

All Superinterfaces:
EventListener
All Known Subinterfaces:
DomainParticipantListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
DomainParticipantAdapter, PublisherAdapter
public interface PublisherListener extends EventListener
Since a Publisher is a kind of Entity, it has the ability to have a listener associated with it. In this case, the associated listener must be of concrete type PublisherListener.
